  "texts": [
    "Our search encompassed research studies from diverse sources, including conferences, journals, and arXiv.",
    "Specifically, we focused on papers published in conferences ranked as A, and journals ranked as Q1 or at least Q2.",
    "However, despite not being published in a conference or journal, we made an exception for a notable work that garnered over 500 citations since 2017 [16].",
    "A summary of the most representative methods under consideration is reported here.",
    "We have taken into consideration 29 methods: (a) We will begin with XAI methods employing a post hoc approach, offering global explanations, and maintaining model agnosticism."
  ]
}